I liked it more than previously. I think the "I am woman" scene is great, one of the best in the movie, and last night I also enjoyed all of them dancing to Liza Minelli's "Single ladies" performance. It's like good junk food, as a lot of movies are.

The card thing reminded me of our transportation card, which you can use to validate your rides on transportation.
